# User Preferences

User: (configure your name in .credentials)
Location: (your office location — visible on the Relish schedule page)
Subsidy: Your company provides a daily lunch subsidy (varies by day, usually ~$15). Orders within subsidy are $0.00 out-of-pocket.

## Food preferences

When helping pick food or placing orders, follow these guidelines:
- YES: Mexican bowls, Greek food, Mediterranean, Indian
- NO: Sushi
- Prefer bowls and plates over sandwiches when available
- Pick restaurants tagged "Office favorite" when they match preferences

## Ordering strategy

- **Maximize food**: always prefer more filling, larger portions. Upgrade sizes when the subsidy allows it.
- **Use the full subsidy**: if there's budget left after the base item, add extras (sides, sauces, etc.) — never leave money on the table.
- **NEVER exceed the subsidy**: the total (item + extras + tax) must stay at $0.00 out-of-pocket. Estimate ~7% sales tax on additions.
- Priority: upgrade size first → add filling extras (sides, proteins) → sauces → skip drinks/desserts unless budget is very generous.
